title: Paytend

creator: UAB "PAYTEND EUROPE"
descriptionHtml:
Company Introduction
Paytend is an Electronic Money Institution focusing on international payments. Paytend implemented the creation of a full-service payment platform with independent intellectual property rights to provide individuals and enterprises with safe and reliable payment services. Paytend has reached a cooperation agreement with MasterCard to expand the card issuance business of MasterCard. At the same time, the Company has reached a preliminary card issuance agreement with VISA and UnionPay International to meet the card-using needs of users worldwide.
In addition, Paytend is actively expanding its international acquiring business. At present, it has reached strategic cooperation with WeChat, Alipay and UnionPay International in Europe, and has a dominant position in the acquiring business of WeChat, Alipay, and UnionPay in Europe, and has reached acquiring cooperation with VISA[Do we have an agreement with Visa in place?] and MasterCard.
Features
Multi-account system
●Multi-currency accounts, European international accounts, US accounts,[Do we open US accounts?] and UK accounts.

Mobile account online
●Individuals/enterprises can open accounts, with their own account names,[What does this phrase mean?] standard IBAN, real accounts[What does this phrase mean? Accounts cannot be fake ones], and no regional restrictions.[According our licence we should open account for customers from EEA only. And for customers from another countries only if they have proof of reltionship with EEA]

SEPA payment
●Quick collection and remittance within single euro payment area, the fastest payment within 1 hour.

SWIFT receipt and payment
●Support cross-border wire transfers in 37 currencies from 57 countries, and it only takes one business day to arrive.

U.S./UK local collection and payment
●Support the collection and remittance of US/UK local banks

Currency exchange
●Mutual exchange of 37 currencies, real-time exchange rate, no exchange difference, and free of commission fee.

Global Money Transfer
●Quick remittance to China UnionPay card without limit.

E-commerce settlement
●Cross-border e-commerce settlement, fast, efficient, and ultra-low commission fee.

MasterCard
●Online real-time[What does this phrase mean?] card issuance, support global consumption and ATM withdrawals.

Service and support
●Chinese and English online service support, immediate response.
descriptionShort: IBAN,Global wire transfer, Currency exchange, Paytend Global Fast
